  "detailed_description": "<h1>Feature List</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214180/extras/6febe91b05a4a8dc13527b8469d7f03a.avif?t=1766232588\" width=484 height=113 /></span><br>-154 Skills<br>-Customize your quest run -- harder and more enemies but better rewards <br> -Spend your earned gold to upgrade your favorite Heroines<br>-Mow down hordes of enemies <br> <br>-Select from 7 unique Heroines <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214180/extras/91ac1288c1d82e37e970cab5a3ebe16a.poster.avif?t=1766232588\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214180/extras/91ac1288c1d82e37e970cab5a3ebe16a.webm?t=1766232588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214180/extras/91ac1288c1d82e37e970cab5a3ebe16a.mp4?t=1766232588\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>-Pass Quests to earn more gold</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214180/extras/b6287f58413d7370a8bcc0c5f43524b4.poster.avif?t=1766232588\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214180/extras/b6287f58413d7370a8bcc0c5f43524b4.webm?t=1766232588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214180/extras/b6287f58413d7370a8bcc0c5f43524b4.mp4?t=1766232588\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>-Combine Job Class skills to obtain more powerful skills<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214180/extras/ca8f022dd3c9f4f38e3824c2413a6e97.poster.avif?t=1766232588\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214180/extras/ca8f022dd3c9f4f38e3824c2413a6e97.webm?t=1766232588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214180/extras/ca8f022dd3c9f4f38e3824c2413a6e97.mp4?t=1766232588\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>-Visit the Court Mage's shop<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214180/extras/4f68a01e65e1a606a50fa49a6049b6ff.poster.avif?t=1766232588\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214180/extras/4f68a01e65e1a606a50fa49a6049b6ff.webm?t=1766232588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214180/extras/4f68a01e65e1a606a50fa49a6049b6ff.mp4?t=1766232588\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Unlock and equip 37 Runestones to improve stats and skills or gain new abilities</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214180/extras/a667f68a60ec742c973920e333b1f78f.poster.avif?t=1766232588\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214180/extras/a667f68a60ec742c973920e333b1f78f.webm?t=1766232588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214180/extras/a667f68a60ec742c973920e333b1f78f.mp4?t=1766232588\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose one of the summoned heroine candidates and dive into an isekai world on the brink of destruction. Collect items, complete posted quests, upgrade your stats and learn new powerful spells in this Action Roguelite with addictive gameplay loop and attractive heroines. Finally, defeat the Demon Lord conqueror and his army of monsters and save the world.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214180/extras/c5c753cde0baba2330ebfc4e5a7323b1.poster.avif?t=1766232588\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214180/extras/c5c753cde0baba2330ebfc4e5a7323b1.webm?t=1766232588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214180/extras/c5c753cde0baba2330ebfc4e5a7323b1.mp4?t=1766232588\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214180/extras/ffd6320af6f64f5e68c665d5728a42ea.poster.avif?t=1766232588\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214180/extras/ffd6320af6f64f5e68c665d5728a42ea.webm?t=1766232588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214180/extras/ffd6320af6f64f5e68c665d5728a42ea.mp4?t=1766232588\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
